# Tool workflow 

## R visualization packages for graphing data
Multiple R librarries are integrated for multiple purposes.

| Package Name   | Description                                                                                     |
|----------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| ggplot2        | General graphing package                                                                        |
| RColorBrewer   | Color palettes, including colorblind-friendly palettes                                       |
| vcfR           | Manipulating VCF data                                                                           |
| sf             | Manipulating spatial vector data                                                                |
| gggenomes      | Comparative genomics                                                                            |
| gggenes        | Gene arrow maps                                                                                 |
| genoPlotR      | Gene and genome maps                                                                            |
| ggseqlogo      | Sequence logos                                                                                  |

